A fully software-based waste classification system that uses Artificial Intelligence to automatically identify and sort waste into **biodegradable** and **non-biodegradable** categories through image processing and deep learning.

## ğŸ” About the Project

This project addresses the inefficiencies in manual and hardware-based waste segregation methods by offering a **cost-effective, scalable, and sustainable** AI-powered solution. It uses a pre-trained **Convolutional Neural Network (CNN)** model and computer vision techniques to classify images of trash.

