- ğŸ§  AI-based image classification (CNN model)
- ğŸ–¼ï¸ User interface for uploading waste images
- ğŸ§ª Visual simulation of virtual waste sorting
- ğŸ“Š Classification confidence and analytics display
- â˜ï¸ Lightweight deployment using **Streamlit** or **Flask**
- ğŸ§ª Thoroughly tested: unit, integration, performance, and stress tests

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: Streamlit / Flask
- **Backend**: Python
- **Libraries**: TensorFlow, OpenCV, NumPy
- **Datasets**: [TACO](https://tacodataset.org/), [TrashNet](https://github.com/garythung/trashnet)

